## Running the App

The app must be served over HTTP (not opened directly as a file) for PubMed scanning and font loading to work correctly.

### Windows
```cmd
cd %USERPROFILE%\Downloads
python -m http.server 8080
```
Then open: [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080)

### Mac / Linux
```bash
cd ~/Downloads
python3 -m http.server 8080
```
Then open: [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080)

### Node.js (any platform)
```bash
npx serve .
```
Then open: [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)

> **Note:** Python is required for the local server. If `python` is not recognized, download it from [python.org](https://www.python.org/downloads/) and check **"Add Python to PATH"** during installation.

