## Using the Publication Alerts

1. Click the **🔔 Publication Alerts** button in the top-right of the app header
2. Set your preferred **date range** (how far back to search)
3. Set your **minimum impact factor** (papers below this threshold are filtered out)
4. Click **Scan All Products** — the app will query PubMed for every product
5. Results appear sorted by impact factor when the scan completes (~2–3 minutes for all products)
6. A red dot appears on the alert button if any IF 10+ papers are found

Scans use the NCBI PubMed E-utilities API with a small delay between requests to respect NCBI rate limits.

